==球风==
[[File:Kylian_Mbappe_2017.jpg|thumb]]与葡萄牙球星[[克里斯蒂亞諾·羅納度|克里斯蒂亞諾·羅納度]]相提并论]]
法国籍足球教练[[阿尔塞纳·温格|-{zh-hans:温格;zh-hk:雲加;zh-tw:溫格;}-]]评价姆巴佩为“与[[蒂埃里·亨利|亨利]]有相似之处”的“巨大的足球天才”<ref name=Arsene>{{cite news|url=http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/762620/Kylian-Mbappe-Arsene-Wenger-Thierry-Henry-Arsenal-Transfer-News-Rumours-Gossip|title=Arsene Wenger confirms bid for French striker|newspaper=Daily Express|accessdate=2018-07-28|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621093124/https://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/762620/Kylian-Mbappe-Arsene-Wenger-Thierry-Henry-Arsenal-Transfer-News-Rumours-Gossip|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在2018年世界杯上代表法国队比赛时，其才华和表现也使他在媒体上与贝利相提并论<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thestar.com/sports/worldcup/2018/06/24/frances-kylian-mbappe-emerges-as-star-in-world-cup-spotlight.html |title=France’s Kylian Mbappe emerges as star in World Cup spotlight |publisher=The Toronto Star |author1=John Leicester |date=2018-06-24 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712020617/https://www.thestar.com/sports/worldcup/2018/06/24/frances-kylian-mbappe-emerges-as-star-in-world-cup-spotlight.html |archive-date=2018-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。姆巴佩经常处于[[前锋_(足球)|边锋]]的位置。<ref name="better than Henry">{{cite web |url=https://www.sportsnet.ca/soccer/elliott-management-becomes-new-owner-ac-milan/ |title=Monaco teen star Mbappe doing better than Henry at same age |publisher=Sportsnet |date=2017-02-20 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711224544/https://www.sportsnet.ca/soccer/elliott-management-becomes-new-owner-ac-milan/ |archive-date=2018-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2017/oct/10/france-didier-deschamps-mbappe-lacazette-griezmann |title=Who should play up front for France? It's time for Didier Deschamps to decide |publisher=The Guardian |author1=Adam White |author2=Eric Devin |date=2017-10-10 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711235330/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2017/oct/10/france-didier-deschamps-mbappe-lacazette-griezmann |archive-date=2018-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，还能够从右侧助攻，为队友创造机会<ref name="wonderkid">{{cite web |url=http://www.squawka.com/en/news/mbappe-v-rashford-v-dembele-which-wonderkid-has-had-the-biggest-impact-so-far-analysis/992850#KuWFV8jCQWxgrEra.97 |title=Mbappe v Rashford v Dembele: Which wonderkid has had the biggest impact so far? |publisher=Squawka |author1=Muhammad Butt |date=2017-09-21 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711225432/http://www.squawka.com/en/news/mbappe-v-rashford-v-dembele-which-wonderkid-has-had-the-biggest-impact-so-far-analysis/992850#KuWFV8jCQWxgrEra.97 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-04-20/next-worlds-best-footballer-griezmann-neymar-mbappe-dybala/8456558 |title=Are Cristiano Ronaldo and Lionel Messi still the world's best footballers? The players breathing down their necks |publisher=ABC.net |author1=James Maasdorp |date=2017-04-20 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914080858/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-04-20/next-worlds-best-footballer-griezmann-neymar-mbappe-dybala/8456558 |archive-date=2017-09-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="going home">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2017/aug/29/kylian-mbappe-paris-saint-germain-neymar |title=Kylian Mbappé going home to Paris with sights on Neymar partnership |publisher=The Guardian |author1=Igor Mladenovic |date=2017-08-29 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712004746/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2017/aug/29/kylian-mbappe-paris-saint-germain-neymar |archive-date=2018-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，他还可以以主力前锋在中锋位置上发挥<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/kylian-mbapp-transfer-news-monaco-caen-goals-real-madrid-arsenal-interest-a7639651.html |title=Kylian Mbappé determined to stay grounded despite Real Madrid leading the race for his signature |publisher=The Independent |author1=Luke Brown |date=2017-03-20 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716062909/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/kylian-mbapp-transfer-news-monaco-caen-goals-real-madrid-arsenal-interest-a7639651.html |archive-date=2018-07-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.foxsportsasia.com/football/731484/mbappe-havent-played-striker-ages/ |title=Mbappe: I haven’t played striker for ages |publisher=www.foxsportsasia.com |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712033535/https://www.foxsportsasia.com/football/731484/mbappe-havent-played-striker-ages/ |archive-date=2018-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Mbappe at 19">{{cite web |url=http://www.beinsports.com/my/ligue-1/news/mbappe-at-19-the-fantastic-french-teenagers-7/740018 |title=Mbappe at 19: The fantastic French teenager's rapid rise |publisher=www.beinsports.com |date=2017-12-20 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712001650/http://www.beinsports.com/my/ligue-1/news/mbappe-at-19-the-fantastic-french-teenagers-7/740018 |archive-date=2018-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="promessa">{{cite web |author1=Piero Faltoni |title=Kylian Mbappé, promessa mantenuta |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.it/piero-faltoni/kylian-mbappe-promessa-mantenuta_a_22079686/ |publisher=Huffington Post |accessdate=2018-07-11 |language=it |date=2017-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711224700/https://www.huffingtonpost.it/piero-faltoni/kylian-mbappe-promessa-mantenuta_a_22079686/ |archive-date=2018-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。作为一名技术娴熟的球员，他的爆发性加速、敏捷、腿脚灵活和创造性而闻名。他还会运用假动作，或者在一对一的情况下突然改变速度或方向以击败对手<ref name="swapping">{{cite web |url=https://www.squawka.com/en/news/how-kylian-mbappes-game-has-changed-since-swapping-monaco-for-psg/1025380#wLgFiQWzAdz60L2c.97 |title=How Kylian Mbappé’s game has changed since swapping Monaco for PSG |publisher=Squawka |author1=Jake Entwistle |date=2018-03-30 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712003147/https://www.squawka.com/en/news/how-kylian-mbappes-game-has-changed-since-swapping-monaco-for-psg/1025380#wLgFiQWzAdz60L2c.97 |archive-date=2018-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="world at his feet">{{cite web |url=https://www.independent.ie/sport/soccer/world-cup-2018/fixtures-and-results/kylian-mbappe-the-19yearold-with-the-world-at-his-feet-37104947.html |title=Kylian Mbappe: The 19-year-old with the world at his feet |publisher=The Irish Independent |date=2018-07-11 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711225645/https://www.independent.ie/sport/soccer/world-cup-2018/fixtures-and-results/kylian-mbappe-the-19yearold-with-the-world-at-his-feet-37104947.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://sport24.lefigaro.fr/football/ligue-1/actualites/sprint-dribbles-feintes-l-action-affolante-de-mbappe-face-a-lille-859278 |script-title=fr:Sprint, dribbles, feintes : L’action affolante de Mbappé face à Lille |publisher=Le Figaro |language=fr |date=2015-05-15 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711230345/http://sport24.lefigaro.fr/football/ligue-1/actualites/sprint-dribbles-feintes-l-action-affolante-de-mbappe-face-a-lille-859278 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。尽管姆巴佩身材瘦高，但他依然具备较强的身体力量<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/juventus-monaco-championsl-league-semifinals-kylian-mbappe-the-sky-is-the-limit-051017 |title=How good is Kylian Mbappe? The teenager just spent 180 minutes torching the best defense in the world |publisher=Fox Sports |author1=Aaron West |date=2017-05-10 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711225412/https://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/juventus-monaco-championsl-league-semifinals-kylian-mbappe-the-sky-is-the-limit-051017 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

除了球技外，姆巴佩灵巧的跑动和通过插入对方空档（不论是否有球时）突破对方防线的能力而备受推崇。他的移动能力可以让他牵制对方防守阵型，同时也使他在反击时对对手造成强大的威胁<ref name="wonderkid"/><ref name="world at his feet"/><ref name="platform">{{cite web |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/world-cup-2018-france-vs-argentina-blaise-matuidi-kylian-mbappe-lionel-messi-a8426281.html |title=World Cup 2018: How Blaise Matuidi laid the platform for Kylian Mbappe to put in the performance of the tournament |publisher=The Independent |author1=Michael Cox |date=2018-07-02 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711210700/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/world-cup-2018-france-vs-argentina-blaise-matuidi-kylian-mbappe-lionel-messi-a8426281.html |archive-date=2018-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.squawka.com/en/news/petit-mbappe-is-ahead-of-henry-in-terms-of-how-he-uses-the-ball-when-running/926918#msAwIATBSQpfAoqS.97 |title=Mbappe’s dribbling skills are superior to Henry’s at the same age – Petit |publisher=Squawka |author1=Jeorge Bird |date=2017-03-31 |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712000203/http://www.squawka.com/en/news/petit-mbappe-is-ahead-of-henry-in-terms-of-how-he-uses-the-ball-when-running/926918#msAwIATBSQpfAoqS.97 |archive-date=2018-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。前法国国脚[[尼古拉斯·阿内尔卡|-{zh-hans:阿内尔卡;zh-hk:安歷卡;zh-tw:安耐卡}-]]评价姆巴佩称：“他让我想起[[1996年亚特兰大奥运会|1996年亚特兰大奥运会]]时的[[罗纳尔多|罗纳尔多]]，他具有世界级球员的特点，而且他必须好好地利用它们。如果他跟随“O Phenomenon”罗纳尔多的职业生涯，他将成为这项运动历史的传奇之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tribalfootball.com/articles/anelka-tells-real-madrid-target-mbappe-be-like-ronaldo-not-me-4178742#XdFSuK2FDHzp3H2i.99|title=Anelka tells Real Madrid target Mbappe: Be like Ronaldo, not me|publisher=Tribal Football|author1=|date=|accessdate=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630185758/http://www.tribalfootball.com/articles/anelka-tells-real-madrid-target-mbappe-be-like-ronaldo-not-me-4178742#XdFSuK2FDHzp3H2i.99|archive-date=2018-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

